creator: Wallet Union
descriptionHtml:
With Wallet you can enjoy full benefits of electronic cards, passes, tickets, coupons and boarding passes on Android. Designed to fully support iOS Passbook and Wallet standards, now you can manage all your passes in your phone.

This application does not support scanning of plastic loyalty cards or paper tickets and converting them into electronic wallet forms.

Main features

* Full compatibility with passes issued for iOS Passbook and Wallet platforms
* Automatic pass update
* Clear change notifications on any updates
* Visual highlights of changed fields
* Allows publishing of native app on the pass
* Notifications based on geo position, iBeacon and relevant time
* Support for QR, PDF417, Aztec and Code 128 barcodes
* One-click installation and pass import
* Built-in QR scanner to import passes
* Backup and restore via Google Drive
* Pass grouping by pass type and issuer
* Card stack arrangements via Drag & Drop
* Pass import via email and file system
* Pass export to email and MMS

Please note that this application is not intended for scanning plastic loyalty cards or paper tickets and converting such plastic or paper into electronic wallet forms. To install electronic loyalty cards and/or electronic tickets, please scan dedicated QR codes leading to electronic versions of the tickets/loyalty cards/boarding passes etc, or look for "Install into Wallet" links/buttons. Those QR/links are created and published by electronic passes' issuers such as retail shops, airlines, event organisers etc.
descriptionShort: Enables full support for iOS Passbook and Wallet electronic passes for Android

- Google Drive support improved
- Some additional fixes and improvements

title: Wallet

creator: Wallet Union
descriptionHtml:
With Wallet you can enjoy full benefits of electronic cards, passes, tickets, coupons and boarding passes on Android. Designed to fully support iOS Passbook and Wallet standards, now you can manage all your passes in your phone.

This application does not support scanning of plastic loyalty cards or paper tickets and converting them into electronic wallet forms.

Main features

* Full compatibility with passes issued for iOS Passbook and Wallet platforms
* Automatic pass update
* Clear change notifications on any updates
* Visual highlights of changed fields
* Allows publishing of native app on the pass
* Notifications based on geo position, iBeacon and relevant time
* Support for QR, PDF417, Aztec and Code 128 barcodes
* One-click installation and pass import
* Built-in QR scanner to import passes
* Backup and restore via Google Drive
* Pass grouping by pass type and issuer
* Card stack arrangements via Drag & Drop
* Pass import via email and file system
* Pass export to email and MMS

Please note that this application is not intended for scanning plastic loyalty cards or paper tickets and converting such plastic or paper into electronic wallet forms. To install electronic loyalty cards and/or electronic tickets, please scan dedicated QR codes leading to electronic versions of the tickets/loyalty cards/boarding passes etc, or look for "Install into Wallet" links/buttons. Those QR/links are created and published by electronic passes' issuers such as retail shops, airlines, event organisers etc.
